    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 06 — Data Annotation Workflow\n\n**Webhook payload format:**\n```json\n{\n  \"csv_data\": \"<base64 encoded CSV>\",\n  \"job_id\": \"job_001\",\n  \"label_schema\": \"positive, negative, neutral, irrelevant\"\n}\n```\n\n**Airtable setup:**\nCreate a base with a table called 'Annotations' with columns: text, label, confidence, job_id, annotated_at, status\n\n**Confidence threshold:** Items < 0.75 confidence are tagged 'needs_review'",
        "height": 724,
